Virtual X68000 User-Visible Changes

$Date: Sun, 15 Aug 1999 00:12:45 +0900 $

Version 0.36

* Changes in M68000 core

** Common condition codes are implemented.

** 708 instruction handlers are implemented though some do not update
the condition codes properly.

** It is close to run DIS source code generator for itself.

* Changes in X68000 machine layer

** Text VRAM can display characters in a window.

** TRAP #15 handler is implemented.

* Changes in Human68k DOS layer

** 27 DOS-call handlers including stubs are implemented

** Memory management is implemented.

** Executable loader can load HU (*.x) executables.

